AECS — AvizSazeh Engineering UX System

NOTE: Structured Figma specification (non-binary format)

=========================================================
1. PAGE STRUCTURE
=========================================================

[1] RFQ HERO SECTION
- Title: Define Your Engineering Project
- Subtitle: Submit architectural data for system-level analysis
- Visual: industrial blueprint background
- CTA: Start Project Definition

[2] RFQ INTRO SYSTEM
- explanation: not a contact form
- definition: project engineering intake system

[3] PROJECT TYPE SELECTION
- ceiling system type
- building category
- project scale

[4] SYSTEM CLASSIFICATION ENGINE
- linear system
- grid system
- custom system
- hybrid system

[5] TECHNICAL INPUT SYSTEM
- area (m²)
- architectural constraints
- structural notes
- environment conditions

[6] FILE UPLOAD ENGINE
- DWG upload
- PDF plans
- reference images

[7] ENGINEERING REVIEW REQUEST
- notes section
- complexity declaration
- priority level

[8] SUBMISSION ENGINE
- "Submit for Engineering Analysis"

